Package: pkgbuild
Title: Find Tools Needed to Build R Packages
Version: 1.0.3
Authors@R: c( person("Hadley", "Wickham", role = "aut"), person("Jim",
    "Hester", , "james.hester@rstudio.com", role = c("aut", "cre")),
    person("RStudio", role = "cph") )
Description: Provides functions used to build R packages. Locates
    compilers needed to build R packages on various platforms and
    ensures the PATH is configured appropriately so R can use them.
